title: Opie & Jim Norton JUL 07 2015 Tue.mp3
description:
THANKS TO @SternGeek FOR THE FILE

On Today's Show: Robert Kelly & Ricky Gervais.


We start the show discussing the Grateful Dead, Robert Kelly joins the show, we talk about oral sex, Amy Schumer apologizes for an old joke, Jim goes to see the new Terminator movie, and we talk about Jurassic World. 

We discuss talking on the phone, Bill Cosby admitted to drugging a woman in 2005, a man had a 6-day erection, Dr. Steve calls in to talk about erections, Jared from Subway's home is raided during a child porn investigation, the quarterback from FSU is caught on video punching a girl, Ricky Gervais joins the show, we debate racism, and Colin Quinn calls in. 

We talk about Ricky's old band and watch a video, we discuss the Yulin Dog Meat Festival, and we wrap up with Ricky
